msgid "Cooks food and keeps bees happy."
msgstr "모닥불은 음식을 조리하고 벌들을 행복하게 유지합니다."

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_campfires/api.lua:115 mods/ITEMS/mcl_campfires/api.lua:161
msgid ""
"Campfires have multiple uses, including keeping bees happy, cooking raw meat "
"and fish, and as a trap."
msgstr ""
"모닥불은 벌들을 행복하게 하고, 생고기와 생선을 요리하며, 덫으로도 사용됩니다."

